branchCategory.name: 11/22-MHR3
branchCategory.description: Series 11/22-M(D)HR3, a 3-finger rotary actuated clean series gripper, features high precision centering and high repeatability.  A double acting rotary actuator and precision ball bearings permit smooth action without vibration.  This series is applicable for clean room class 10.
